    "Now if M, x ⊩ □ i φ and xR i y, so M, y ⊩ φ, then y ′ ⊑ y and Persistence together imply M, y ′ ⊩ φ.",
    "Thus, according to our interpretation of R i, we should be able to have xR i y ′.The condition up-R is not necessary for Persistence.",
